{
  "stem": "1680.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he came-- and he noticed too-- so he came there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he schlepped-- my wife had a raincoat with a hat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He pulls her out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I saw from far-- I didn't know exactly that's her, but I saw that he grabbed somebody.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I knew that's the area where Margot was standing there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the meantime, he realized, and he didn't take her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He the other one and shot her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because she threw it over-- a butter-- a pound of butter over the fence.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She figured maybe after this he goes out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She's going to get it back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was another incident.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you remember what you were thinking at that time?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was thinking-- I was-- in the beginning, I was almost sure that's Margot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when I saw that they took her, pulled her out and tossed the fence, so I saw that's not Margot.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then-- then came the high holidays.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They always managed during the high holidays to make some incidents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah, and before things in November of 1939, they start burning the synagogues.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On one Sunday, all of the sudden-- we were sitting in the house, and all of the sudden we see fire all over.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we start looking out, and there was every synagogue in the city was burnt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was nighttime.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The city was light up like daylight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was so light.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they burnt the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was in November 1939 still.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I jumped over to '42.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
